Description: Group words into different classes by using the 'Brown' word clustering algorithm. 
    Wraps the C++ library available at <https://github.com/chrisquirk/brown-cluster>.
    The techniques are explained in detail in the paper 'Class-Based n-gram Models of Natural Language' by Brown et al. (1992) <https://www.aclweb.org/anthology/J92-4003.pdf>.
